伊朗疫情坏消息频出：卫生部副部长确诊、死亡率超高、防控经验匮乏。
The Iranian epidemic is fraught with bad news: the Deputy Minister of Health is diagnosed, mortality is extremely high, and prevention and control experience is poor.
李静 曹然。
Li Jing Cao Ran.
中国新闻周刊                      。
China News Weekly.
中国新闻周刊。
